$(OL

$(LI
对于相等性比较， $(C rhs) 属非$(C null) 并且成员相等就足够了：

---
enum Color { blue, green, red }

class Point {
    int x;
    int y;
    Color color;

// ...

    override bool opEquals(Object o) const {
        const rhs = cast(const Point)o;

        return rhs && (x == rhs.x) && (y == rhs.y);
    }
}
---

